column5: Good morning all,  just want to wish all who participate in the up coming deer gun season good luck shoot straight and most of all be safe!!!  I will be heading out Saturday morning to our camp in South River for the week!!!    Peps
Good luck to you out there. Have a safe trip.
I saw two deer on my way home from work.  Right on Tiffen st in Barrie. Just off the 400.  Good luck next week.  I had to cancel my plans because of work..  argh..
Headed up for the second week myself - all the best and hunt safe.  Dan
Good Luck and be safe  painted this a while ago---so everyone would remember what they looked like  Sorry boys---gotta better shot of it here
Leaving tonight for deer wonderland Good luck to all Leechman
Yes, Good Luck all!!  Not preaching - but I heard an awful story this year during moose..  Small reminder. Be aware of your target and beyond - Be Safe.
I might,get out for a day during the second week.First year I havent hunted in 10 years.
im heading north on sunday for a week..... looking forward to it
Aim small...miss small...  But the most important is tree stand safety.......more hunters are killed and or seriously injured because they fall out of their tree stands.   BE VERY CAREFUL   Bob
